{% render 'section-new-faq-clothing-styles-min' %}
<div class="section-container">
                <h2 class="faq-title hero__overlay-title section-title has-animated">
                    Clothing Featured Questions
                </h2>
            <div class="new-faq_wrapp">
                <div class="new-faq_item">
                    <div class="new-faq_item-title">
                        <p class="font-title">
                            How much does it cost to get my clothes authenticated?
                        </p>
                        <a href="javascript:void(0)"  class="font-title">
                            +
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="new-faq_item-text">
                        <p class="font-description">
                            The price of our luxury clothes authentication generally falls within the range of $15 to $50, which can vary depending on factors such as the brand and desired turnaround time.
<br><br>
For instance, if you need to authenticate a Balenciaga hoodie within a 30-minute timeframe, the cost would be $35. However, if you are able to wait for 12 hours, the fee for authenticating the same hoodie would be just $15.
<br><br>
Ultimately, the pricing is influenced by the specific time constraints and the brand associated with your clothing. It's worth noting that higher-end and prestigious brands tend to command higher authentication costs.
</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="new-faq_item">
                    <div class="new-faq_item-title">
                        <p class="font-title">
                            How can I authenticate my luxury clothes?
                        </p>
                        <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="font-title">
                            +
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="new-faq_item-text">
                        <p class="font-description">
                            You can choose to authenticate your clothing by yourself. Genuine luxury clothes have distinct features that counterfeit ones cannot replicate, depending on the brand, production year, and specific model. It is crucial to concentrate on these unique characteristics to determine the authenticity of your clothes.
<br><br>
Our specialized guides are available for reference and offer detailed instructions on how to authenticate different brands. These guides include a comprehensive checklist that can assist you in reaching an authenticity determination with a 99% accuracy rate.
<br><br>
Nevertheless, we strongly recommend you leveraging LegitGrails’s authentication experts if you want an accurate opinion. 
</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="new-faq_item">
                    <div class="new-faq_item-title">
                        <p class="font-title">
                           How long does it take to authenticate luxury clothes?
                        </p>
                        <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="font-title">
                            +
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="new-faq_item-text">
                        <p class="font-description">
                           Depending on how fast you need the results, you can choose from our 24-hours, 12-hours, 2 hours, or 30 minutes authentication. If you’re in a hurry, we recommend choosing our 30-minute or 2 hours authentication. If you can wait for 6 or 12 hours, choose one of these options to get a better price. 
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
            </div>
  <div class="new-faq_bottom font-title">
      <p>Have more questions? Visit our <a href="https://legitgrails.frontkb.com/en">Help Center</a></p>
  </div>
        </div>

